<plot>Set in Dhaka, Bangladesh, the story follows Aasia Begum in her Rickshaw garage as she explains the trials and tribulations she has gone through in her life from being a house maid to becoming a Rickshaw garage owner. This is a moving and inspiring documentary about one woman's determination and also her reluctance to give up in a man's world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?020698</url></doc>
